我从源码中并没有看到ConsumerContextFilter.invoke中放入group属性

下面是我重写了ConsumerContextFilter，会调用super.invoke(invoker, invocation)
```
@Activate(group = CommonConstants.CONSUMER)
@Configuration
@Slf4j
public class DubboContextFilter extends ConsumerContextFilter {

    @Override
    public Result invoke(Invoker<?> invoker, Invocation invocation) throws RpcException {
        String langLocale = LocaleContextHolder.getLocale().toString();
        if (langLocale != null) {
            RpcContext.getContext().setAttachment("lang_locale", langLocale);
        }
        String requestId = MDC.get("requestId");
        if(requestId!=null){
            RpcContext.getContext().setAttachment("requestId", requestId);
        }
        Result invoke = super.invoke(invoker, invocation);
        String serverIp = invoke.getAttachment("serverIp");
        if(StringUtils.isNotEmpty(serverIp)){
            log.info("serverIp:{},method:{}.{}",serverIp,invoker.getInterface().getName(),invocation.getMethodName());
        }
        
        return invoke;
    }
}
